Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.84,0:00:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪刀和瓦楞紙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次在這裏讓我看看那時的絕技吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕技？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒~ 看看也沒啥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是雜耍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 小氣鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿看到了卜部的裸體對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 和卜部一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時看到的漂亮裸體就會在腦裏浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想會各種糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不妙哦 對男生來說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為卜部的裸體太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.97,0:01:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就偷拍了一張
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係啦 絕對不會給別人看的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是只屬於我的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 給我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不給
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只拍了一張對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帥…帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且剪刀是夾在內褲上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看看讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 居然在這種地方夾剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺真色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 沒啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自星之瞳文化節以來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣跟卜部一起走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候看到的卜部的裸體就會浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:04:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要壓制不禁想去抱住旁邊的卜部這種衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時的日課
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可以舔一下椿的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我的…口水？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不行 今天不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺身體發熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口撲通直跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別問我理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體還很燙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口也撲通直跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿看到了卜部的裸體對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 和卜部一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時看到的漂亮裸體就會在腦裏浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想會各種糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像真的可以看到裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼椿 今天就到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 頭有點晃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的卜部又…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准隨便抱過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種程度的擦傷 用手帕擦擦就會自然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了 手帕沒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 不管它血也自然會止住的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好消毒處理的話 說不定會留下傷痕的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫你處理傷口 現在能馬上來我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 卜部的家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 進來吧 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去準備急救箱 能去我房間等一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明只瞄準了相框的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然連窗簾也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久違的卜部的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的床
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枕頭…有點濕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有種甜甜的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 我幫你消毒額頭的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把劉海撩起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我平時用剪刀是不會失手的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天卻讓椿受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒啥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是擦傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過確實很少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為昨天我做了奇怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想那個就是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的夢是怎樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才碰了卜部的枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有點濕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道那個和奇怪的夢有關？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 卜部的臉變紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔舔看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 感覺好像又看到卜部的裸體了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 腦袋恍惚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要抱卜部了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口處理還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不要靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要撲到卜部身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隨便抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須改變方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 眼看要撲到床上去 拚命改變方向就撞上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改變方向？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要改變方向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是就那樣倒在床上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會抱住卜部了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會受傷的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種時候抱住我也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,額頭的傷需要冷敷一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿冰塊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天椿受的傷都是因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 不介意的話能不能告訴我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部昨天做的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎樣的夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和椿…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我？然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後面的不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次窗簾沒有剪到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來剪刀的手感恢復原樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才抱著椿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些模糊的心情感覺變得舒暢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有昨天做的夢的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿雖然很好色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很好色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部 等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是做夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好軟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的額頭怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女朋友無論如何都要剪我的劉海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓她用剪刀剪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准心有點偏了 或者說是失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我摔了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那個紗布昨天開始就沒換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗布要每天都換的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女朋友無論如何都要給我處理傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托她的福 我的房間都是紗布的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那究竟是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對是在模仿卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就別客氣 拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諏訪野？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中老師讓你現在馬上到職員室去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,職員室？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是升學的咨詢調查
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟我們是負責傳單的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脫下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 我帶了創可貼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些紗布怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諏訪野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的紗布能還給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫你扔了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你額頭的紗布…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要脫掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是明明換成創可貼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:20:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得卜部的紗布更能促進傷口癒合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想 這個紗布是卜部擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了我而貼的紗布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話 我想用到不能再用為止什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 今天的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 剛才突然手就過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用內褲剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我想被椿抱住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 椿 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都謎團重重的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觸碰到卜部的心的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常地高興
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第13話
